import { Route, BrowserRouter as Router, Switch } from "react-router-dom";

// Homepage
import OneShare from "./pages/home/index";

// Onboard
import SignIn from "./pages/onboard/sign-in.js";
import SignUp from "./pages/onboard/sign-up.js";

// Dashboard


function App() {
  return (
    <Router>
      <Switch>
        
        <Route path="/" exact component={OneShare} />
        <Route path="/sign-in" exact component={SignIn} />
        <Route path="/sign-up" exact component={SignUp} />

      </Switch>
    </Router>
  );
}

export default App;

<Provider store={store}>
			<PersistGate persistor={persistor}>
				<Router>
					<Switch>
						<Route path={url.home} exact component={LandingPage} />
						<Route path={url.aboutUs} exact component={AboutUs} />
						<Route path={url.bugReport} exact component={BugReport} />
						<Route path={url.digiStore} exact component={DigiStore} />
						<Route path={url.ourTeam} exact component={OurTeam} />
						<Route path={url.portfolio} exact component={Portfolio} />
						<Route path={url.privacy} exact component={Privacy} />
						<Route path={url.suggestFeature} exact component={SuggestFeature} />

						{/*  */}
						<Route path={url.signIn} exact component={SignIn} />
						<Route path={url.signUp} exact component={SignUp} />
						<Route path={url.fgtPwd} exact component={ForgotPassword} />
						<Route path={url.pwdReset} exact component={PasswordReset} />
						<Route path={url.verifyEmail} exact component={VerifyEmail} />
						{/* public profile  */}
						<Route path={url.home_profile} exact component={Home} />
						<Route path={`${url.contact_profile}`} exact component={Contact} />
						<Route path={`${url.project_profile}`} exact component={Project} />
						<Route path={`${url.resume_profile}`} exact component={Resume} />
						{/* Dashboard Screen */}
						<Route path={url.dashHome} exact component={HomeBoard} />
						<Route path={url.addEditSocial} exact component={SocialBoard} />
						<Route path={url.chngePass} exact component={ChangePassword} />
						<Route path={url.projAdd} exact component={ProjectBoard} />

						<Route path={url.settingView} exact component={SettingsBoard} />
						<Route path={url.addNewSKill} exact component={SkillsBoard} />
						<Route path={url.accountEdit} exact component={AccountEditBoard} />
						{/*  */}
						<Route path={url.addView} exact component={AddViewBoard} />
						<Route path={url.resumeView} exact component={ResumeViewBoard} />
						<Route path={url.projView} exact component={ProjectViewBoard} />
						<Route path={url.addNewSKill} exact component={SkillsBoard} />
						<Route path={url.addNewCustomSKill} exact component={CustomCard} />
						{/*  */}
						<Route path={url.addWork} exact component={WorkForm} />
						<Route path={url.addEducation} exact component={EducationForm} />
						{/* error page */}
						<Route path='' component={ErrorPage} />
					</Switch>
				</Router>
			</PersistGate>
		</Provider>
